BrightBlade, Rage

* BrightBlade sighed as she felt her pelt finally dry from the day's sun, 
she stood up stiffly but then shock to relieve it. She looked around the 
clearing a bit but then back at the lake, could Gangon still be under there? 
She shrugged but then began to plod away towards the Predacon base, her 
home.*

^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^

* Rage growled as she plodded through the forest, she had smelled fresh 
blood only a few moments before and it had caused her stomach to growl as 
well. But what she didn't know was that she was stalking the exact same prey 
that both Tavatron and Dinobot were, it was just a matter of time until 
either met up with the other!*
